<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Notification: Reply to Your Question</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #000428, #004e92);
            color: #fff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #00171f;
            border-radius: 7px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #f0f0f0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        p {
            color: #ccc;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #007bff;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .container {
                width: 80vw;
                padding: 10px;
                background-color: #00171f;
            }
            h1, h2, p {
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
        .copyright {
            color: #999;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Notification</h1>
        <p>Hello <%= user.name %>,</p>
        <p>Someone has replied to your question in the video "<%= title %>" on the platform. To view the reply, please login to the platform.</p>
        <p>Thank you for being an active member of our community!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="copyright">
        &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Course Cosmos. All rights reserved.
    </div>
</body>
</html>
